  <entry>
    <title>烂大街的排序算法总结_python代码风骚版</title>
    <url>/2020/02/05/%E7%83%82%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%97%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93-python%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E9%A3%8E%E9%AA%9A%E7%89%88/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>编程的空间是无比广阔的。—-尼古拉斯~沃尔硕德<br> <a id="more"></a></p>
<h3 id="此代码版本极尽风骚，个中滋味，自行体会"><a href="#此代码版本极尽风骚，个中滋味，自行体会" class="headerlink" title="此代码版本极尽风骚，个中滋味，自行体会"></a>此代码版本极尽风骚，个中滋味，自行体会</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">1.冒泡排序 </span><br><span class="line">时间复杂度：O(n^2),空间复杂度：O(1)</span><br><span class="line">今日重温发现之前写的思路废话太多，冒泡排序的思路其实很简单，先选出一个最大的，而后选出一个次大的，而后选出一个次次大的。。。</span><br><span class="line">不得不说，那个swap是点睛之笔</span><br><span class="line">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">def bubble_sort(arr):</span><br><span class="line">    length &#x3D; len(arr)</span><br><span class="line">    for i in range(length - 1):</span><br><span class="line">        swap &#x3D; False</span><br><span class="line">        for j in range(length - 1 - i):</span><br><span class="line">            if arr[j] &gt; arr[j+1]:</span><br><span class="line">                swap &#x3D; True</span><br><span class="line">                arr[j],arr[j+1] &#x3D; arr[j+1],arr[j]</span><br><span class="line">        if not swap:break</span><br><span class="line">    return arr</span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">2.插入排序 </span><br><span class="line">时间复杂度：O(n^2),空间复杂度：O(1)</span><br><span class="line">思路：整个序列看成有序和无序，起初，将第一个数字同后面“隔开”，这样左边为有序，</span><br><span class="line">右边为无序，然后要做的就是从无序中一个个的取出数字插入到有序中</span><br><span class="line">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">def insertion_sort(arr):</span><br><span class="line">    length &#x3D; len(arr)</span><br><span class="line">    for i in range(1,length):</span><br><span class="line">        while arr[i - 1]&gt; arr[i] and i &gt; 0:</span><br><span class="line">            arr[i - 1],arr[i] &#x3D; arr[i],arr[i - 1]</span><br><span class="line">            i -&#x3D; 1</span><br><span class="line">    return arr</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">3.快速排序 </span><br><span class="line">时间复杂度：O(nlogn),空间复杂度：O(logn)</span><br><span class="line">思路：选定一个值为基准值，将序列中所有小于他的值放在一边，所有大于</span><br><span class="line">他的值放在另一边，然后分别在得到的两边中递归方才的过程，最终实现排序操作</span><br><span class="line">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">def quick_sort(arr):</span><br><span class="line">    length &#x3D; len(arr)</span><br><span class="line">    if length &lt;&#x3D; 1:</span><br><span class="line">        return arr</span><br><span class="line">    pivot &#x3D; arr[0]</span><br><span class="line">    greater &#x3D; [item for item in arr[1:] if item &gt; pivot]</span><br><span class="line">    lesser &#x3D; [item for item in arr[1:] if item &lt;&#x3D; pivot]</span><br><span class="line">    return quick_sort(lesser) + [pivot] + quick_sort(greater)    </span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">4.选择排序 </span><br><span class="line">时间复杂度：O(nlogn),空间复杂度：O(logn)</span><br><span class="line">思路：每次便利扫描出最小的那个数，内循环结束，交换值。</span><br><span class="line">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">def selection_sort(arr):</span><br><span class="line">    length &#x3D; len(arr)</span><br><span class="line">    for i in range(length - 1):</span><br><span class="line">        least &#x3D; i</span><br><span class="line">        for k in range(i+1,length):</span><br><span class="line">            if arr[k] &lt; arr[least]:</span><br><span class="line">                least &#x3D; k</span><br><span class="line">        arr[least],arr[i] &#x3D; arr[i],arr[least]</span><br><span class="line">    return arr</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">5.希尔排序 </span><br><span class="line">思路：隔几个进行插入排序</span><br><span class="line">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">def shell_sort(arr):</span><br><span class="line">    gaps &#x3D; [701, 301, 132, 57, 23, 10, 4, 1]</span><br><span class="line">    for gap in gaps:</span><br><span class="line">        i &#x3D; gap</span><br><span class="line">        while i &lt; len(arr):</span><br><span class="line">            j &#x3D; i</span><br><span class="line">            while arr[j - gap] &gt; arr[j] and j &gt;&#x3D; gap:</span><br><span class="line">                arr[j - gap],arr[j] &#x3D; arr[j],arr[j - gap]</span><br><span class="line">                j -&#x3D; gap</span><br><span class="line">            i +&#x3D; 1                </span><br><span class="line">    return arr</span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">6.归并排序 </span><br><span class="line">思路：一句话，分而治之</span><br><span class="line">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line"># version 1</span><br><span class="line">def merge_sort(arr):</span><br><span class="line">    start &#x3D; []</span><br><span class="line">    end &#x3D; []</span><br><span class="line">    while len(arr) &gt; 1:</span><br><span class="line">        a &#x3D; min(arr)</span><br><span class="line">        b &#x3D; max(arr)</span><br><span class="line">        start.append(a)</span><br><span class="line">        end.append(b)</span><br><span class="line">        arr.remove(a)</span><br><span class="line">        arr.remove(b)</span><br><span class="line">    if arr:start.append(arr[0])</span><br><span class="line">    end.reverse()</span><br><span class="line">    return (start + end)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># version 2</span><br><span class="line">def merge_sort_sec(arr):</span><br><span class="line">    length &#x3D; len(arr)</span><br><span class="line">    if length &gt; 1:</span><br><span class="line">        midpoint &#x3D; length &#x2F;&#x2F; 2</span><br><span class="line">        left_half &#x3D; merge_sort_sec(arr[:midpoint])</span><br><span class="line">        right_half &#x3D; merge_sort(arr[midpoint:])</span><br><span class="line">        i &#x3D; 0</span><br><span class="line">        j &#x3D; 0</span><br><span class="line">        k &#x3D; 0</span><br><span class="line">        while i &lt; len(left_half) and j &lt; len(right_half):</span><br><span class="line">            if left_half[i] &lt; right_half[j]:</span><br><span class="line">                arr[k] &#x3D; left_half[i]</span><br><span class="line">                i +&#x3D;1</span><br><span class="line">            else:</span><br><span class="line">                arr[k] &#x3D; right_half[j]</span><br><span class="line">                j +&#x3D;1</span><br><span class="line">            k +&#x3D; 1</span><br><span class="line">        while i &lt; len(left_half):</span><br><span class="line">            arr[k] &#x3D; left_half[i]</span><br><span class="line">            i +&#x3D; 1</span><br><span class="line">            k +&#x3D; 1</span><br><span class="line">        while j &lt; len(right_half):</span><br><span class="line">            arr[k] &#x3D; right_half[j]</span><br><span class="line">            j +&#x3D; 1</span><br><span class="line">            k +&#x3D; 1</span><br><span class="line">    return arr</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"># -----------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">7.堆排序 </span><br><span class="line">时间复杂度：O(nlogn),空间复杂度：O(logn)</span><br><span class="line">思路：两步走战略，首先，构建一颗大堆树，即最大值在根节点，随后，将根节点</span><br><span class="line">值和最后节点值交换，而后对除最大值的剩余值重复先前操作</span><br><span class="line">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br><span class="line">def heapify(arr,index,heap_size):</span><br><span class="line">    largest &#x3D; index</span><br><span class="line">    left_index &#x3D; 2 * index + 1</span><br><span class="line">    right_index &#x3D; 2 * index + 2</span><br><span class="line">    if left_index &lt; heap_size and arr[left_index] &gt; arr[largest]:</span><br><span class="line">        largest &#x3D; left_index</span><br><span class="line">    if right_index &lt; heap_size and arr[right_index] &gt; arr[largest]:</span><br><span class="line">        largest &#x3D; right_index</span><br><span class="line">    if largest !&#x3D; index:</span><br><span class="line">        arr[index],arr[largest] &#x3D; arr[largest],arr[index]</span><br><span class="line">        heapify(arr,largest,heap_size)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">def heap_sort(arr):</span><br><span class="line">    n &#x3D; len(arr)</span><br><span class="line">    for i in range(n &#x2F;&#x2F;2 - 1,-1,-1):</span><br><span class="line">        heapify(arr,i,n)</span><br><span class="line">    for i in range(n-1,0,-1):</span><br><span class="line">        arr[0],arr[i] &#x3D; arr[i],arr[0]</span><br><span class="line">        heapify(arr,0,i)</span><br><span class="line">    return arr</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">user_input &#x3D; input(&#39;please input numbers seperated by a comma:&#39;)</span><br><span class="line">arr &#x3D; [int(item) for item in user_input.split(&#39;,&#39;)]</span><br><span class="line">print(*bubble_sort(arr),sep &#x3D; &#39;,&#39;)</span><br><span class="line">print(*insertion_sort(arr),sep &#x3D; &#39;,&#39;)</span><br><span class="line">print(*quick_sort(arr),sep&#x3D;&#39;,&#39;)</span><br><span class="line">print(*selection_sort(arr),sep&#x3D;&#39;,&#39;)</span><br><span class="line">print(*shell_sort(arr),sep&#x3D;&#39;,&#39;)</span><br><span class="line">print(*merge_sort_sec(arr),sep&#x3D;&#39;,&#39;)</span><br><span class="line">print(*heap_sort(arr),sep&#x3D;&#39;,&#39;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
